sentences.english: How can they control what pops up on the Internet?
sentences.chinese: 他們能否控制互聯網上的彈出消息？

sentences.english: Enable the item specified by id in the popup menu.
sentences.chinese: 開啓彈出式選單中指定代碼的項目。

sentences.english: When you select a station, the map zooms in, and ashort message pops up.
sentences.chinese: 當你選到一個站點，地圖被放大，一條短消息被彈出。

sentences.english: You should see Operation completed successfully in a pop-up dialog:.
sentences.chinese: 您將在彈出對話框中看到操作成功完成。

sentences.english: Can You Pop an Abscessed Tooth?
sentences.chinese: 你能彈出一個牙牀膿腫？。

sentences.english: If you find the popup distracting, you can move the slider to Never.
sentences.chinese: 如果你發現彈出框影響了你，你可以讓其消失不再見。

sentences.english: Don't let blinking icons and pop-ups disrupt your work flow.
sentences.chinese: 不要讓閃爍的圖標和彈出的窗口打斷你的工作流程。

sentences.english: Once you believe, then it’s on and popping like popcorn.
sentences.chinese: 一旦你相信，它就會像爆米花一樣“砰”地彈出來。

sentences.english: Toggles popup information window for the pointed entry in the playlist.
sentences.chinese: 切換播放列表中鼠標指向的項的彈出信息窗口。

sentences.english: Please make sure you turn off your pop-up blocker.
sentences.chinese: 請確保您關閉您的彈出窗口攔截器。

sentences.english: These cute little Tic Tacs of color are popping up all over the design world.
sentences.chinese: 這些色彩和彈出的可愛小把戲遍佈了整個設計界。

sentences.english: You can post new messages from pop-up page after clicking the button.
sentences.chinese: 點擊按鈕後，你可以在彈出視窗直接發送新的訊息。

sentences.english: Turn off any pop-up blockers you may have on your PC.
sentences.chinese: 關閉你的個人電腦上有關窗口彈出的限制。

sentences.english: You are a Qingcui string, string that pops up on the melody is love.
sentences.chinese: 您是一根輕脆的琴絃，弦上彈出的旋律是愛。

sentences.english: Click on the window and it comes up, ready for use.
sentences.chinese: 點擊窗口，窗口就會彈出來，等待使用。

sentences.english: The Search Results page still features pop-up links to the manufacturers' Web sites.
sentences.chinese: 查找結果頁面仍然包含能連接到廠商網站的彈出鏈接。
